<p> </p>
<p><img alt="header_small_update" src="/images/stories/header_small_update.jpg" height="135" width="580" /></p>
<p> </p>
<p>Great news!</p>
<p> </p>
<p>We have sent everyone who voted in the last two years an invitation for this years voting and we already collected in less than <strong>24 hours more than 30,000 votes</strong>. We also contacted all the companies involved in the voting and got great feedback.</p>
<p> </p>
<p>They also pointed out some minor mistakes we corrected, mostly grammar or graphical but we also had to change one game that did not met all regulations. We changed the game <strong>The Mummy Online</strong> from Bigpoint to <strong>Pirate Storm</strong> also from Bigpoint. The change was made because <strong>The Mummy Online</strong> was not developed in Europe.</p>
<p> </p>
<p><a href="/index.php?option=com_wrapper&amp;view=wrapper&amp;Itemid=8"><img alt="the_mummy_online" src="/images/stories/gamecovers/2012/the_mummy_online.jpg" height="250" width="450" /></a></p></td>
</tr>

